                src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/icons/896639829415178240/f14ab7a63eaf0c302ac31cafae536ff1.png?size=4096"
                width="60px">
              <h6 class="partner-title d-inline-block">Eternity <img id="Partner" class="verified-badge"
